reviewText:
A great concert experience. Here is what Descarga says: Live concert held at an intimate club setting in Colombia. With Diego Gale and his band backing up the powerfull singer. Maelo performs his hits like "Regalame Una Noche," "No Mas Mentiras," "Deseo" and many others -- and he sounds terrific. Otra vez... Maelo Ruiz.
Good quality multi-camera production. Recommended
